reviews.review_text:
Smiles All Around A nice town tucked into the hills of Virginia and no hassles. Great show. Band members smiles all around.
When they open with Finiculi Finicula, it's going to be a good night. Rare West LA 2nd set opener.
Nothing but great memories. Same the next night.
